{"tid":2045821,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國七名前外相促為香港局勢設國際監察小組","createTime":"2020-06-01T04:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T05:40:55.000Z","uid":241764,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2f9ce6378158063b28298ac30d1ebcbb812df28f","tid":2045821,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:39:38.000Z","msg":"英國七名來自保守黨和工黨的前任外相發表公開信，促請英國首相約翰遜推動七國集團，就中國制訂「國安法」加強控制香港，成立國際監察小組。<br />\n<br />\n包括夏偉林、聶偉敬、侯俊偉、文禮彬、貝嘉晴、施仲宏和歐文等七名前外相，向現任外相藍韜文發信，他們呼籲約翰遜與七國集團聯繫，成立國際聯絡小組，監測香港局勢並協調聯合行動。他們認為可以仿傚1990年代，英、美、法、德、意大利和俄羅斯，就巴爾幹危機成立的小組。<br />\n<br />\n七國領袖原下月會面，但美國總統特朗普表示，將推遲舉行峰會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529518-20200601.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529518-20200601.htm&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=7a6ef886\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529518-20200601.htm&h=f6c94e24\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529518-20200601.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b930a4745f39da7e26af21e3ed11faef8da879ae","tid":2045821,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:46:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c0173f7f2d13c782807482a7e667cdf5384eda1","tid":2045821,"uid":44199,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:49:29.000Z","msg":"見到Jeremy Cunt個名就....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1fb80ddc1e16e00e53268db41ed2636f18b89e","tid":2045821,"uid":52228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T05:40:55.000Z","msg":"希望佢哋有所行動啦"}]}